# {{COMPANY_NAME}} Website

Corporate homepage generated by AI Team Framework.

## Stack

- Next.js
- React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

## Getting Started

```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open `http://localhost:3000`.

## Pages

- `/`
- `/about`
- `/services`
- `/contact`

## Generated Context

Generation metadata and maintenance guidance are stored in `.ai-team/`.

- `.ai-team/core/`: framework-managed guidance.
- `.ai-team/user/`: project-specific notes and overrides.
- `.ai-team/manifest.json`: generator and update metadata.

Write custom project context in `.ai-team/user/`. Future framework updates must not overwrite that directory.

## Where To Edit

- Company info: `lib/site-config.ts`
- Homepage: `app/page.tsx`
- About page: `app/about/page.tsx`
- Services page: `app/services/page.tsx`
- Contact page: `app/contact/page.tsx`
- Header: `components/site-header.tsx`
- Footer: `components/site-footer.tsx`
- Theme: `tailwind.config.ts`
